author: mprudhom
msg: The recent upgrade of maven-jar-plugin to 2.1 caused the Implementation-Version tag to be excluded from the manifest, which we rely on to detect the current version. Added "addDefaultSpecificationEntries" and "addDefaultImplementationEntries" to pluginManagement to fix this.
